tions\\n44: \\n45: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n46: \\n47: ## Design Decisions\\n48: \\n49: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n50: \\n51: ## Alternatives Considered\\n52: \\n53: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n54: \\n55: ## Implementation Status\\n56: \\n57: ### 已完成\\n58: \\n59: [To be filled during implementation]\\n60: \\n61: ## Testing Strategy\\n62: \\n63: ### Unit Tests\\n64: \\n65: [To be filled during implementation]\\n66: \\n67: ### Integration Tests\\n68: \\n69: [To be filled during implementation]\\n70: \\n71: ## Configuration\\n72: \\n73: ### 环境变量\\n74: \\n75: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n76: \\n77: ## API Specification\\n78: \\n79: [To be filled d...\n  Line 40: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862962120,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286539de0ffeA96R5fMXgNP0FG\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79ae57a10010xbAKcKqVwRY0h\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ae3a24001SxPmh5IUqXx8f1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286539de0ffeA96R5fMXgNP0FG\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-ba1f12c150034b36b426e2ed6423c669\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Proposal: AR-018 — Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: Agentd 空闲清理控制器是一个 Kubernetes 控制器，用于自动检测和清理 AgentCube 平台中的空闲或废弃的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 资源。该控制器通过监控资源活动状态和生命周期事件，基于可配置的空闲超时策略执行清理操作，帮助优化资源利用率，防止资源泄漏，并维护系统健康。\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 在 `pkg/agentd` 模块中实现空闲清理控制器，通过 client-go 库监控和管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 自定义资源，自动检测并清理长期空闲的资源，减少手动运维负担，提升集群资源利用效率。\\n10: \\n11: ## Module\\n12: \\n13: `pkg/agentd`\\n14: \\n15: ## Language\\n16: \\n17: Go 1.25\\n18: \\n19: ## Size\\n20: \\n21: S\\n22: \\n23: ## Scope\\n24: \\n25: ### In Scope\\n26: \\n27: 1. **控制器实现** (`pkg/agentd/controller/idle_cleanup.go`)\\n28:    - 实现 Kubernetes 控制器框架和协调循环\\n29:    - 控制器注册和生命周期管理\\n30:    - 空闲超时阈值配置\\n31:    - 优雅关闭处理\\n32: \\n33: 2. **空闲检测逻辑**\\n34:    - 使用 client-go informers 监控 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 资源\\n35:    - 跟踪最后活动时间戳、状态条件和生命周期事件\\n36:    - 基于可配置策略评估空闲状态：\\n37:      - N 分钟内无 pod/执行活动\\n38:      - 完成/失败状态持续 N 分钟\\n39:      - 孤立资源（无匹配的父/所有者引用）\\n40: \\n41: 3. **清理操作**\\n42:    - 删除空闲的 AgentRuntime 资源\\n43:    - 删除空闲的 CodeInterpreter 资源\\n44:    - 事件日志记录用于审计和可观测性\\n45:    - 可选的 Kubernetes 事件通知\\n46: \\n47: 4. **配置**\\n48:    - 空闲超时值的命令行标志\\n49:    - 针对目标清理的可配置标签选择器\\n50:    - 干运行模式支持用于测试\\n51: \\n52: 5. **测试**\\n53:    - 空闲检测逻辑的单元测试\\n54:    - 使用 fake clientset 的集成测试\\n55:    - 使用模拟 Kubernetes API 的端到端测试\\n56: \\n57: ### Out of Scope\\n58: \\n59: - 垃圾回收依赖的 pod、PVC 或其他子...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-018_ST-4.log:\n  Line 6: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862872621,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79acf1ba001CqGQ1ty5GfN03j\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ace07b001aJNQYeEJE3x7sy\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_9001f8900da741a4b0515486\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"find /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z -type f -name \\\"*.md\\\" | grep -i \\\"ar-018\\\\|agentd\\\\|task\\\" | head -20\",\"description\":\"Find AR-018 related markdown files\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/picod/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/agentd/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sand