\n12: \\n13: #### Scenario: Start idle cleanup controller\\n14: \\n15: - **GIVEN** a configured `IdleCleanupController` with `Enabled = true`\\n16: - **WHEN** `Start(ctx)` is called during agentd initialization\\n17: - **THEN** the controller SHALL start periodic cleanup cycles at `CleanupInterval` and watch resource events\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: Stop controller gracefully\\n20: \\n21: - **GIVEN** a running `IdleCleanupController`\\n22: - **WHEN** `Stop()` is called during shutdown\\n23: - **THEN** the controller SHALL stop watching resources and complete in-flight clea...\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862881118,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79ad05d30010HYu2Y0ynfXR3T\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79acfa61001ma1bCukfMSm5yb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_7e21cbb7f4ac41aa8337d9a3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Proposal: Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller (AR-018)\\n2: \\n3: ## Summary\\n4: \\n5: Implement an idle cleanup controller in `pkg/agentd` that automatically identifies and terminates idle AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources based on configurable inactivity timeouts, releasing cluster resources and maintaining system hygiene.\\n6: \\n7: ---\\n8: \\n9: ## Purpose\\n10: \\n11: The Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller provides:\\n12: \\n13: 1. **Resource Reclamation**: Automatically clean up idle agent runtimes and code interpreters to free cluster resources\\n14: 2. **Configurable Idle Detection**: Support per-resource-type idle timeout configuration\\n15: 3. **Graceful Termination**: Properly finalize resources before deletion with status updates\\n16: 4. **Observability**: Emit metrics and logs for cleanup operations\\n17: 5. **Safe Operation**: Respect resource11s and avoid cleaning resources with active workloads\\n18: \\n19: This implementation builds upon the client-go infrastructure from `deployment/client-go.md` and integrates with the workload manager's reconciliation loop to ensure cleaned resources are properly handled.\\n20: \\n21: ---\\n22: \\n23: ## Scope\\n24: \\n25: ### In Scope\\n26: \\n27: - `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go` - Idle cleanup controller interface and implementation\\n28: - `pkg/agentd/idle_tracker.go` - Idle state tracking...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862887743,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79ad2e6c001A9n2DlMKHNkSEL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ad1b97001c6jJ4GO0xG1ctC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_6cc2e3a88551420099e8f315\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"mkdir -p /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/src\",\"description\":\"Create src directory for AR-018\"},\"output\":\"\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"\",\"exit\":0,\"description\":\"Create src directory for AR-018\",\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Create src directory for AR-018\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775862887720,\"end\":1775862887739}}}}\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862980473,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79ad3e69001nLY5OsaOUNx5wL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ad3572001ajD1JrzcU9HP60\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28653205affeCYrhnPGU1oCRmh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_58343438d29a4fd18ae83da7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_202604