## Task Breakdown\\n9: \\n10: ### Task 1: Verify pkg/agentd directory structure\\n11: - [ ] Verify pkg/agentd directory exists\\n12: - [ ] Create pkg/agentd directory if missing\\n13: - [ ] Verify controller.go exists\\n14: - [ ] Verify controller_test.go exists\\n15: - [ ] Verify constants.go exists\\n16: - [ ] Verify metrics.go exists (optional)\\n17: \\n18: **Verification**: Run `ls -la pkg/agentd/` and verify all required files exist\\n19: \\n20: ---\\n21: \\n22: ### Task 2: Verify constants.go defines required constants\\n23: - [ ] Verify SessionExpirationTimeout constant is defined (15 * time.Minute)\\n24: - [ ] Verify LastActivityAnnotationKey constant is defined (\\\"last-activity-time\\\")\\n25: - [ ] Verify DefaultRequeueInterval constant is defined (30 * time.Second)\\n26: - [ ] Verify time package is imported\\n27: - [ ] Verify constants have proper documentation comments\\n28: - [ ] Verify constant values match design specifications\\n29: \\n30: **Verification**: Review constants.go implementation and verify all constants are correctly defined\\n31: \\n32: ---\\n33: \\n34: ### Task 3: Verify Reconciler struct definition in controller.go\\n35: - [ ] Verify Reconciler struct embeds ...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862713796,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79aa8b450012J5CjBKEGFynKV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79aa7cd6001gaZPg2oQLiBBku\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-ab32302d380f4ce480b3d0228ca7a570\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\\n2: \\n3: ## 模块信息\\n4: \\n5: - **模块**: `pkg/agentd`\\n6: - **语言**: Go\\n7: - **规模**: S\\n8: - **关联需求**: AR-018\\n9: \\n10: ## 架构概述\\n11: \\n12: ### 设计目标\\n13: \\n14: Agentd 是一个 Kubernetes 控制器，负责监控和管理 AgentCube 中的 Sandbox 资源的空闲状态。当 Sandbox 资源在配置的超时时间内没有活动时，Agentd 自动清理该资源，释放计算资源，防止资源浪费。\\n15: \\n16: ### 核心组件\\n17: \\n18: ```\\n19: pkg/agentd/\\n20: ├── controller.go         # Reconciler 主控制器实现\\n21: ├── controller_test.go    # 控制器单元测试\\n22: ├── constants.go          # 常量定义（超时时间、注解键等）\\n23: └── metrics.go            # Prometheus 指标采集（可选）\\n24: ```\\n25: \\n26: ### 架构原则\\n27: \\n28: 1. **被动监控**: 通过 Kubernetes Informer 机制被动监听 Sandbox 资源变更\\n29: 2. **延迟调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度，避免频繁轮询\\n30: 3. **幂等性**: 所有操作都是幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\\n31: 4. **最小干扰**: 只在必要时触发清理操作，减少对正常运行中的 Sandbox 的影响\\n32: 5. **注解驱动**: 通过注解进行状态通信，与 workload-manager 协同工作\\n33: \\n34: ## 组件设计\\n35: \\n36: ### Reconciler 控制器\\n37: \\n38: #### 数据结构\\n39: \\n40: ```go\\n41: package agentd\\n42: \\n43: import (\\n44:     \\\"context\\\"\\n45:     \\\"time\\\"\\n46: \\n47:     \\\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\\\"\\n48:     \\\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\\\"\\n49:     \\\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\\\"\\n50:     agentsv1alpha1 \\\"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\\\"\\n51: )\\n52: \\n53: type Reconciler struct {\\n54:     client.Client\\n55:     S...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862713799,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79aa8d9c001VXZKjr67R6r2jx\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79aa7cd6001gaZPg2oQLiBBku\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-b348929161f6465d92750574ca880172\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_2