理控制器\\n2: \\n3: ## Metadata\\n4: - **AR**: AR-018\\n5: - **Title**: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\\n6: - **Module**: pkg/agentd\\n7: - **Language**: Go\\n8: - **Size**: S\\n9: - **Status**: Pending\\n10: \\n11: ## Description\\n12: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n13: \\n14: ## Dependencies\\n15: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n16: \\n17: ## Related Changes\\n18: [To be filled during spec definition]\\n\\n(End of file - total 18 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\\n\\n## Metadata\\n- **AR**: AR-018\\n- **Title**: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\\n- **Module**: pkg/agentd\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: S\\n- **Status**: Pending\\n\\n## Description\\n[To be filled during spec definition]\\n\\n## Dependencies\\n[To be filled during spec definition]\\n\\n## Related Changes\\n[To be filled during spec definition]\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/CHANGE.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775862763243,\"end\":1775862763249}}}}\n  Line 57: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862765521,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79ab57aa001r2pHF55mIa8MuD\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ab4f21001GCWYGzXvnxsDbv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-c6f20c9058cb46bfba86cf1d209a55a7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-018 Delta Specification: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 实现 agentd 模块的空闲清理控制器，当 `Sandbox` 自定义资源在指定的空闲超时时间内没有活动时，自动清理（删除）该资源。该控制器监控 `last-activity-time` 注解，在超过 15 分钟无活动后删除对应的 Sandbox 资源。\\n6: \\n7: ## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\\n8: \\n9: ## Delta Overview\\n10: \\n11: 新增空闲清理控制器功能，包括 `Reconciler` 实现、controller-runtime Manager 配置、以及 `cmd/agentd/main.go` 二进制程序入口。系统监控 `Sandbox` 资源的变化，读取 `last-activity-time` 注解，计算空闲时间，当超过 `SessionExpirationTimeout`（15 分钟）时删除 Sandbox 资源。\\n12: \\n13: ---\\n14: \\n15: ## Reconciler 实现\\n16: \\n17: ### Requirement: Reconciler 结构体定义\\n18: \\n19: 系统 SHALL 提供 `Reconciler` 结构体封装控制器逻辑，嵌入 controller-runtime 的 `client.Client` 和持有 `runtime.Scheme`。\\n20: \\n21: ```go\\n22: type Reconciler struct {\\n23:     client.Client\\n24:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\\n25: }\\n26: ```\\n27: \\n28: ### 场景: Reconciler 结构体包含必要字段\\n29: \\n30: **GIVEN** Reconciler 结构体已定义\\n31: **WHEN** 查看结构体字段\\n32: **THEN** 包含嵌入的 client.Client 类型\\n33: **AND** 包含 Scheme 字段（*runtime.Scheme 类型）\\n34: \\n35: ---\\n36: \\n37: ### Requirement: Reconcile 方法签名\\n38: \\n39: 系统 SHALL 提供 `Reconcile` 方法，实现 controller-runtime `Reconciler` 接口。\\n40: \\n41: ```go\\n42: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\\n43: ```\\n44: \\n45: ### 场景: Reconcile 方法符合接口\\n46: \\n47: **GIVEN** Reconciler 结构体...\n  Line 60: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775862785865,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79ab8c1e001ufGRKrf2DZGCCV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ab5808001b9RSDY7ynIV48u\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Based on my review of AR-018 (Agentd 空闲清理控制器), here's the archive summary:\\n\\n## ✅ **What Was Completed**\\n\\n**Core Implementation (Tasks 1-19):**\\n- Complete `pkg/agentd/controller.go` with Reconciler logic\\n- All constants defined in `constants.go`\\n- Full `cmd/agentd/main.go` binary with proper configuration\\n- Proper error handling, logging, and RequeueAfter logic\\n- Scheme registration and controller setup\\n\\n**Comprehensive Testing (Tasks 20-26, 30-31):**\\n- 16 unit tests covering all scenarios (83.6% coverage)\\n- Tests for: NotFound, missing/empty/invalid annotations, expired/not-expired, edge cases\\n- Tests pass successfully\\n- Binary builds without errors\\n\\n**Documentation (Task 36):**\\n- Complete README.md with architecture, configuration, and usage instructions\\n\\n## ⏸️ **What Was Deferred**\\n\\n**Kubernetes Deployment (Tasks 32-34):**\\n- No RBAC ClusterRole manifest created\\n- No ServiceAccount manifest created  \\n- No Kubernetes Deployment manifest created\\n- No RBAC markers in controller.go\\n\\n**Optional Features (Task 29):**\\n- No `metrics.go` with Prometheus metrics (optional per design)\\n\\n**Integration Testing (Tasks 27-28, 37-38):**\\n- No end-to-end integration tests with envtest\\n- No integration tests with workload-manager\\n\\n**Documentation Updates (Task 35):**\\n- CHANGE.md status still shows \\\"Pending\\\" (not updated to Completed)\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\n**Completion Rate**: ~70% (28 of 40 tasks)\\n- ✅ All core functionality and unit tests complete\\n- ⏸️ Kubernetes manifests and integration testing deferred\\n- The controller is fully functional and production-ready code-wise, but lacks deployment artifacts for cluster deployment\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775862785863,\"end\":1775862785863}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-018_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862574937,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28657a10effeJg2rEsldi5zbr1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79a86ab7001JA8nt0OobnK2na\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79a85fdc001xLeP7oO9yVlcv4\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28657a10effeJg2rEsldi5zbr1\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_22db460f76aa479398aa4ed4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T16