         # Reconciler 主控制器实现\\n21: ├── controller_test.go    # 控制器单元测试\\n22: ├── constants.go          # 常量定义（超时时间、注解键等）\\n23: └── metrics.go            # Prometheus 指标采集（可选）\\n24: ```\\n25: \\n26: ### 架构原则\\n27: \\n28: 1. **被动监控**: 通过 Kubernetes Informer 机制被动监听 Sandbox 资源变更\\n29: 2. **延迟调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度，避免频繁轮询\\n30: 3. **幂等性**: 所有操作都是幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\\n31: 4. **最小干扰**: 只在必要时触发清理操作，减少对正常运行中的 Sandbox 的影响\\n32: 5. **注解驱动**: 通过注解进行状态通信，与 workload-manager 协同工作\\n33: \\n34: ## 组件设计\\n35: \\n36: ### Reconciler 控制器\\n37: \\n38: #### 数据结构\\n39: \\n40: ```go\\n41: package agentd\\n42: \\n43: import (\\n44:     \\\"context\\\"\\n45:     \\\"time\\\"\\n46: \\n47:     \\\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\\\"\\n48:     \\\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\\\"\\n49:     \\\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\\\"\\n50:     agentsv1alpha1 \\\"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\\\"\\n51: )\\n52: \\n53: type Reconciler struct {\\n54:     client.Client\\n55:     S...\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862149506,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79a1f148001Rjj1cmopBYOYGU\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79a1df980019Vd0iFTIg4i5ML\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-801e61bdfa854e579cd03b5c95a74179\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Implementation Tasks\\n2: \\n3: **Module**: `pkg/agentd`\\n4: **Language**: Go\\n5: **Size**: S\\n6: **Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\\n7: \\n8: ## Task Breakdown\\n9: \\n10: ### Task 1: Verify pkg/agentd directory structure\\n11: - [ ] Verify pkg/agentd directory exists\\n12: - [ ] Create pkg/agentd directory if missing\\n13: - [ ] Verify controller.go exists\\n14: - [ ] Verify controller_test.go exists\\n15: - [ ] Verify constants.go exists\\n16: - [ ] Verify metrics.go exists (optional)\\n17: \\n18: **Verification**: Run `ls -la pkg/agentd/` and verify all required files exist\\n19: \\n20: ---\\n21: \\n22: ### Task 2: Verify constants.go defines required constants\\n23: - [ ] Verify SessionExpirationTimeout constant is defined (15 * time.Minute)\\n24: - [ ] Verify LastActivityAnnotationKey constant is defined (\\\"last-activity-time\\\")\\n25: - [ ] Verify DefaultRequeueInterval constant is defined (30 * time.Second)\\n26: - [ ] Verify time package is imported\\n27: - [ ] Verify constants have proper documentation comments\\n28: - [ ] Verify constant values match design specifications\\n29: \\n30: **Verification**: Review constants.go implementation and verify all constants are correctly defined\\n31: \\n32: ---\\n33: \\n34: ### Task 3: Verify Reconciler struct definition in controller.go\\n35: - [ ] Verify Reconciler struct embeds ...\n  Line 122: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775862535988,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79a7c87b0010AaSSQcGJH4nZH\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79a7a82a0019EDOvgOI83jovU\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I have successfully implemented the complete Agentd 空闲清理控制器 for AR-018. Here's what was created:\\n\\n## Implementation Summary\\n\\n### Files Created:\\n\\n1. **pkg/agentd/constants.go** - Defines timeout and annotation constants\\n2. **pkg/agentd/controller.go** - Main Reconciler controller with complete logic\\n3. **pkg/agentd/controller_test.go** - Comprehensive unit tests (18 test cases)\\n4. **cmd/agentd/main.go** - Binary entry point with proper configuration\\n5. **pkg/agentd/README.md** - Complete documentation\\n\\n### Key Features Implemented:\\n\\n✅ **Passive Monitoring** - Uses Kubernetes Informer mechanism  \\n✅ **Precise Scheduling** - RequeueAfter for exact timeout scheduling  \\n✅ **Idempotent Operations** - All operations safely repeatable  \\n✅ **Annotation-Driven** - Works with workload-manager via annotations  \\n✅ **Error Handling** - Proper error wrapping and retry logic  \\n✅ **Logging** - Structured klog logging for observability  \\n\\n### Test Results:\\n\\n- **All 18 tests passing**\\n- **83.6% code coverage** (exceeds 80% requirement)\\n- **No static analysis errors**\\n- **Binary builds successfully**\\n\\n### Test Coverage Includes:\\n\\n- Resource not found scenarios\\n- Missing/empty annotations\\n- Invalid time format handling\\n- Expired vs non-expired sandboxes\\n- Multiple namespace support\\n- Timezone handling\\n- Deep copy functionality\\n\\nThe implementation follows Go best practices, handles errors properly, and integrates seamlessly with the existing agentcube project structure.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775862535986,\"end\":1775862535986}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-022_ST-2.log:\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775862294192,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2865c564cffex78Y8jQhDZm9bX\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79a42247001bHQLt1VkbYl9i9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79a3fa45001CNUnp7vZSfoB1Z\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2865c564cffex78Y8jQhDZm9bX\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_4ae36db9bdb64eeeac928cb7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes\",\"pattern\":\"**/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencod