uring design phase]\\n6: \\n7: ## Component Design\\n8: \\n9: [To be filled during design phase]\\n10: \\n11: ## Data Flow\\n12: \\n13: [To be filled during design phase]\\n14: \\n15: ## Sequence Diagrams\\n16: \\n17: [To be filled during design phase]\\n18: \\n19: ## State Management\\n20: \\n21: [To be filled during design phase]\\n22: \\n23: ## Concurrency Model\\n24: \\n25: [To be filled during design phase]\\n26: \\n27: ## Error Handling\\n28: \\n29: [To be filled during design phase]\\n\\n(End of file - total 29 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"# AR-018 Design Document\\n\\n## Architecture Overview\\n\\n[To be filled during design phase]\\n\\n## Component Design\\n\\n[To be filled during design phase]\\n\\n## Data Flow\\n\\n[To be filled during design phase]\\n\\n## Sequence Diagrams\\n\\n[To be filled during design phase]\\n\\n## State Management\\n\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775861822775,\"end\":1775861822815}}}}\n  Line 22: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775861945602,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28663384efferv1Xjt01zePk3j\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d799ed4670015O2e58OhaHbUW9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d799d243c001zizL0YHsVn4Vzz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28663384efferv1Xjt01zePk3j\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-289424595fdc4ff09fde9247c8f249da\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\\n\\n## 模块信息\\n\\n- **模块**: `pkg/agentd`\\n- **语言**: Go\\n- **规模**: S\\n- **关联需求**: AR-018\\n\\n## 架构概述\\n\\n### 设计目标\\n\\nAgentd 是一个 Kubernetes 控制器，负责监控和管理 AgentCube 中的 Sandbox 资源的空闲状态。当 Sandbox 资源在配置的超时时间内没有活动时，Agentd 自动清理该资源，释放计算资源，防止资源浪费。\\n\\n### 核心组件\\n\\n```\\npkg/agentd/\\n├── controller.go         # Reconciler 主控制器实现\\n├── controller_test.go    # 控制器单元测试\\n├── constants.go          # 常量定义（超时时间、注解键等）\\n└── metrics.go            # Prometheus 指标采集（可选）\\n```\\n\\n### 架构原则\\n\\n1. **被动监控**: 通过 Kubernetes Informer 机制被动监听 Sandbox 资源变更\\n2. **延迟调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度，避免频繁轮询\\n3. **幂等性**: 所有操作都是幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\\n4. **最小干扰**: 只在必要时触发清理操作，减少对正常运行中的 Sandbox 的影响\\n5. **注解驱动**: 通过注解进行状态通信，与 workload-manager 协同工作\\n\\n## 组件设计\\n\\n### Reconciler 控制器\\n\\n#### 数据结构\\n\\n```go\\npackage agentd\\n\\nimport (\\n    \\\"context\\\"\\n    \\\"time\\\"\\n\\n    \\\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\\\"\\n    \\\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\\\"\\n    \\\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\\\"\\n    agentsv1alpha1 \\\"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\\\"\\n)\\n\\ntype Reconciler struct {\\n    client.Client\\n    Scheme *runtime.Scheme\\n}\\n\\ntype ReconcileResult struct {\\n    Result reconcile.Result\\n    Error  error\\n}\\n```\\n\\n#### 核心方法\\n\\n```go\\nfunc (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req reconcile.Request) (reconcile.Result, error)\\n\\nfunc (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error\\n```\\n\\n#### 常量定义\\n\\n```go\\npackage agentd\\n\\nimport \\\"time\\\"\\n\\nconst (\\n    // SessionExpirationTimeout 定义空闲会话的超时时间\\n    SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\\n\\n    // LastActivityAnnotationKey ...\n  Line 25: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775861959463,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28663384efferv1Xjt01zePk3j\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d799f0414001C3tyT09N0GtiB4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d799ed54c001HLfs2UP7zh6GNS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28663384efferv1Xjt01zePk3j\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Design document written to `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md`\\n\\nThe design covers:\\n- Architecture overview with core components\\n- Component design with Reconciler structure\\n- Data flow diagrams and detailed steps\\n- Sequence diagrams for key scenarios\\n- State management for Sandbox lifecycle\\n- Concurrency model using Informer mechanism\\n- Error handling strategies\\n- API contracts and RBAC permissions\\n- Testing strategy, deployment config, and monitoring\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775861959461,\"end\":1775861959461}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-018_ST-2.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775861689710,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d799aed34001keKNGbnqgPkegc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d799ae5e1001sBKure0IbqII3P\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-d97fc9b9369e417fa9cf1f6450f63f7f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write delta-spec.md (GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios) for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\\n4: Module: pkg/agentd\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: S\\n7: \\n8: Base specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Clientset\\n15: \\n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\\n17: \\n18: ```go\\n19: type Interface interface {\\n20: \\tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\\n21: \\tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\\n22: }\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### `Clientset` struct\\n26: \\n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\\n28: \\n29: **Constructors**\\n30: \\n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, 