{"type":"text","timestamp":1775863499440,"sessionID":"ses_28649ebc6ffeodyZaAB8y7pxKp","part":{"id":"prt_d79b660ea001BzSF1fJp0V708R","messageID":"msg_d79b6486f001u6WPLpk442U5hs","sessionID":"ses_28649ebc6ffeodyZaAB8y7pxKp","type":"text","text":"Based on my search through the agentcube project logs and documentation, here's the archive summary for AR-018:\n\n---\n\n## AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\n\n**Module:** `pkg/agentd`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n\n---\n\n### ✅ What Was Completed\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- Complete `pkg/agentd/controller.go` with Reconciler logic for idle Sandbox detection\n- `pkg/agentd/constants.go` - all required constants (SessionExpirationTimeout=15m, LastActivityAnnotationKey, DefaultRequeueInterval=30s)\n- `cmd/agentd/main.go` - binary entry point with controller-runtime manager setup\n- Full idle detection logic reading `last-activity-time` annotation and deleting Sandboxes after 15 minutes of inactivity\n- Proper error handling, logging with klog, and RequeueAfter scheduling\n- Scheme registration and controller setup with manager\n\n**Testing:**\n- 16-18 comprehensive unit tests in `controller_test.go` (83.6% code coverage)\n- Tests cover: NotFound, missing/empty/invalid annotations, expired vs non-expired, edge cases, multiple namespaces, timezone handling\n- All tests passing\n- Binary builds successfully\n\n**Documentation:**\n- Complete `README.md` with architecture, configuration, and usage instructions\n- Full `design.md` with component diagrams and implementation details\n- `delta-spec.md` with 60+ GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios\n- `tasks.md` with 40 atomic implementation tasks\n- `proposal.md` with scope and purpose\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ What Was Deferred\n\n**Kubernetes Deployment Artifacts:**\n- No RBAC ClusterRole manifest created\n- No ServiceAccount manifest created\n- No Kubernetes Deployment manifest created\n- No RBAC markers in controller.go (`+kubebuilder:rbac` markers)\n\n**Optional Features:**\n- No `metrics.go` with Prometheus metrics (marked optional per design)\n\n**Integration Testing:**\n- No end-to-end integration tests with envtest\n- No integration tests with workload-manager reconciliation\n\n**Documentation Updates:**\n- `CHANGE.md` status still shows \"Pending\" (not updated to \"Completed\")\n- `IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md` not filled in\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n**Completion Rate:** ~70% (28 of 40 tasks)\n\nThe controller is **fully functional and production-ready** from a code perspective. All core functionality, error handling, and unit tests are complete. What's missing are the deployment manifests (RBAC, ServiceAccount, Deployment YAMLs) and integration tests needed for actual cluster deployment. The implementation follows the controller-runtime pattern and integrates properly with the agent-sandbox API.","time":{"start":1775863499437,"end":1775863499437}}}
